        "title": "Key Expressions",
        "content": "<h3>Documentation is usually optional</h3>\n\n<p>문서화는 대부분 선택 사항이다.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Capture the final result</h3>\n\n<p>최종 결과를 기록하다</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Capture the engineering process</h3>\n\n<p>엔지니어링 과정을 기록하다</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Alternative solutions</h3>\n\n<p>대안 설계</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Architectural choices</h3>\n\n<p>아키텍처 의사결정</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Knowledge retention</h3>\n\n<p>지식 보존</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Long-term maintainability</h3>\n\n<p>장기 유지보수성</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Knowledge generated automatically</h3>\n\n<p>지식이 자동으로 생성된다</p>\n\n<hr>"
